# 60-Day, 60-Project Full Stack + LLM + DS/ML Learning Plan

## Tech Stack:

* Java
* Spring Boot
* JavaScript
* React JS
* Python
* LLM (Large Language Models)
* Data Science & Machine Learning (DS/ML)

---

## Daily Learning Structure

* **1-1.5 hours per tech** (Learn via crash courses or tutorials)
* **2-3 hours per project build** (Hands-on coding)
* **15-30 mins reflection** (Write notes, challenges, GitHub updates)

---

# Detailed Day-by-Day Plan with Resources

## Week 1

### Day 1

**Project:** Basic Calculator CLI
**Tech:** Java + Python
**Resources:**

* Java CLI Tutorial: [https://www.w3schools.com/java/java\_user\_input.asp](https://www.w3schools.com/java/java_user_input.asp)
* Python CLI Basics: [https://realpython.com/python-command-line-arguments/](https://realpython.com/python-command-line-arguments/)

### Day 2

**Project:** Weather API Fetcher
**Tech:** JS + Python
**Resources:**

* JS Fetch API: [https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Fetch\_API](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Fetch_API)
* Python Requests: [https://realpython.com/python-requests/](https://realpython.com/python-requests/)
* Free Weather API: [https://www.weatherapi.com/](https://www.weatherapi.com/)

### Day 3

**Project:** To-Do List Backend API
**Tech:** Spring Boot + Java
**Resources:**

* Spring Boot REST API: [https://spring.io/guides/gs/rest-service/](https://spring.io/guides/gs/rest-service/)

### Day 4

**Project:** To-Do List Frontend
**Tech:** JS + React JS
**Resources:**

* React To-Do Tutorial: [https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/learn-react-by-building-a-simple-to-do-app/](https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/learn-react-by-building-a-simple-to-do-app/)

### Day 5

**Project:** Currency Converter CLI
**Tech:** Java + Python
**Resources:**

* Currency API: [https://exchangerate.host/](https://exchangerate.host/)
* Java API Calls: [https://www.baeldung.com/java-http-request](https://www.baeldung.com/java-http-request)

### Day 6

**Project:** Movie Search App (REST API)
**Tech:** Spring Boot + JS
**Resources:**

* Movie DB API: [https://developers.themoviedb.org/3](https://developers.themoviedb.org/3)

### Day 7

**Project:** Random Joke Generator
**Tech:** Python + React JS
**Resources:**

* Joke API: [https://icanhazdadjoke.com/api](https://icanhazdadjoke.com/api)

